           IF  IN-EXCS-NEW-YN1 = CO-CHA-Y
           THEN
               MOVE CO-CHA-1
                 TO RJLR007-EXCS-NEW-YN1
           ELSE
               MOVE CO-CHA-0
                 TO RJLR007-EXCS-NEW-YN1
           END-IF
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------

      *@   초과신규여부２
           IF  IN-EXCS-NEW-YN2 = CO-CHA-Y
           THEN
               MOVE CO-CHA-1
                 TO RJLR007-EXCS-NEW-YN2
           ELSE
               MOVE CO-CHA-0
                 TO RJLR007-EXCS-NEW-YN2
           END-IF
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------

      *@   초과신규여부３
           IF  IN-EXCS-NEW-YN3 = CO-CHA-Y
           THEN
               MOVE CO-CHA-1
                 TO RJLR007-EXCS-NEW-YN3
           ELSE
               MOVE CO-CHA-0
